Usage: python pypeak.py <ip_bed_file> <control_bed_file>

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -w WINDOW_LENGTH, --window_length=WINDOW_LENGTH
                        scanning window size in bp for each strand:
                        default=135
  -s SIGNAL_THRESHOLD, --signal_threshold=SIGNAL_THRESHOLD
                        signal threshold calling enriched regions: default=5
  -o OUT_FILE, --out_file=OUT_FILE
                        name of the bed file output is written to
  -q, --quiet           don't print status messages to stdout
  -d DIP_THRESHOLD, --dip_threshold=DIP_THRESHOLD
                        dip threshold for splitting enriched regions:
                        default=0.6

